# Commit Message Template
#
# Format: <emoji> <type of commit>: <message>
# Example: ✨ feat: add user login flow
#
# Commit Types and Emojis (Gitmoji Standard):
#
# ✨ feat: New feature
# 🐛 fix: Bug fix
# ♻️ refactor: Code restructuring
# 💄 style: Code style / UI changes (no logic)
# 📝 docs: Documentation only changes
# ✅ test: Add or update tests
# 🚀 deploy: Deploy-related changes
# 🔧 chore: Misc maintenance / config
# 🔨 build: Build system or external dependencies
# ⚙️ ci: CI/CD configuration
# 📦 chore: Add or update dependencies
# 🧪 debug: Debugging code
# 🔒 fix: Security fix
# 🚨 BREAKING CHANGE: Major breaking change
# 💥 BREAKING CHANGE: API breaking change
# 💣 BREAKING CHANGE: Destructive change (e.g. data loss)
# 🗃️ chore: Database-related changes (e.g. migrations)
# ⚡️ perf: Performance improvements
# 🔍 feat: Add analytics or logging
# 🔗 feat: Add routing or links
#
# Write your commit message below this line:
